Sequence File Name      JGI ID  Bin_Number
11340.2.202025.CCAGTGT-AACACTG.fastq.gz 1108358 5
11340.3.202029.AGCTAAC-GGTTAGC.fastq.gz 1108364 6
11340.5.202037.TCATCAC-GGTGATG.fastq.gz 1108376 11
